data.description: Beautiful Georgian styled home in the Chestnut Grove Elem school district. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home features a large, gently sloped backyard that was recently cleared, has a back deck, storage shed and under ground drainage. Inside. you will love the hardwood floors throughout the main living areas. Newer flooring in the kitchen. Specialty ceilings, updated tile shower, formal dining room, natural gas fireplace, and 3 year old HVAC system....there's so much to appreciate about this stately home. Main floor bedroom could be used as an office as well. Call today for your private showing.
